title: One-Pot Mediterranean Leek & Tomato Risotto with Capsicum Relish & Parmesan Cheese
description: We’re sending your tastebuds to paradise with a risotto that is saucy and dancing with hearty veggies like leek and cherry
tomatoes. The capsicum relish stirred through is sure to make you smile, so sit back and enjoy your time with this sunny and
aromatic risotto.
